Package Utils

Class CommandHandler

java.lang.Object
Utils.CommandHandler
Direct Known Subclasses:
GameCommandHandler, MapCommandHandler, PlayerCommandHandler
public abstract class CommandHandler
extends java.lang.Object
An abstract class representing a command handler for game-related commands. This class provides access to the game engine and log entry buffer for command handling.
